{"tid":319263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為食女狀元立志做醫生","createTime":"2017-07-12T16:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T05:18:52.000Z","uid":5195,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"431ec49a6d006c8c5471822c3441fd782c65ae43","tid":319263,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140715/photo/0715-00407-009b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140715%2Fphoto%2F0715-00407-009b1.jpg&h=dd9d9b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n協恩中學的女狀元陳詠妍除了7科考獲5**級外，在數學科的延伸部分亦考獲5**級，成為超級女狀元，對理科有濃厚興趣的她原來是「食得之人」，中五時已開始在社交網站Instagram寫食評，更有逾六百名追隨者，下至街邊數元小食、上至花費數千元的高級法國菜，詠妍也品嘗過，亦饒有心得，「最鍾意食分子料理，覺得好有創意！」冀將來考入醫科，「食好嘢要使錢，都要識搵錢至得。」"},{"pid":"d5cc7d7402265049e8574f8c138544bbe42658c2","tid":319263,"uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:10:26.000Z","msg":"贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4c3485aba4e35d2ed5b72b5cb8bd5741ac616a","tid":319263,"uid":20867,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"歧義句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14cbd4308d09221973e4ad78020b03f86241ca7","tid":319263,"uid":32824,"like":39,"dislike":4,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:13:16.000Z","msg":"睇左<br />\n為 食女 狀元 立志入醫科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f119c721a09232159ae7e9b14172b08857cc56","tid":319263,"uid":66825,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T16:14:58.000Z","msg":"過幾年打扮下應該唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712351cb5dd8a9df994c1ce3930488ca1d2033d6","tid":319263,"uid":35101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT